-- Metorex of South Africa Says Copper, Cobalt Production to Climb This Year
-- Alastair Reed
-- 2010-09-07T05:14:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-07/metorex-of-south-africa-says-copper-cobalt-production-to-rise-this-year.html

          
          
             Metorex Ltd. said cobalt and copper
production for the 12 months through June 2011 is expected to
increase from a year earlier.  
 “This is directly attributable to the commissioning of the
Ruashi mine,” the company said.  
          
          


  


        